&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an Accountant to work at the CaptiveAire corporate office in Raleigh. Reporting to the Chief Financial Officer, this role involves maintaining and managing financial operations to ensure accuracy and compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise day-to-day accounts payable and cash receipts processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct month-end and year-end closures and prepare journal entries and financial statements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and manage the annual budget process and prepare monthly budget reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain accounting controls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS in Accounting required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years of work experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail and accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to learn quickly and work independently with minimal oversight.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Office Word and Excel; strong spreadsheet skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of an accounting information system; experience with Blackbaud software is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidentiality and integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good math skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to adapt to new technologies and multi-task in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivated with a positive attitude and a team player.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is NOT a remote role.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical, dental, and vision insurance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Disability and life insurance based upon election of medical insurance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401k with employer match.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible spending account (FSA).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Competitive salary dependent upon experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Captive-Aire Systems, Inc. is proud to be an equal opportunity workplace. We review applications for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, ancestry, citizenship, age, uniformed services, genetic information, physical or mental disability, medical condition, marital status, or any other basis prohibited by law.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;To qualify, applicants must be legally authorized to work in the United States. At this time, we are not able to consider applicants that require sponsorship, now or in the future, for employment visa status.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Seeking a driven and motivated engineer to join our engineering team focusing on application engineering for our diverse line of HVAC equipment. Application Engineers should be comfortable working in a result-driven, fast-paced environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Application Engineer at CaptiveAire, you will play a key role in shaping, advancing, and supporting innovative HVAC solutions for a wide range of real world applications.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Work for CaptiveAire?&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nation’s leading manufacturer of commercial kitchen ventilation systems, and now offering a complete solution of fans, heaters, ductwork and HVAC equipment.  Our primary purpose is to provide fully integrated, sustainable HVAC Systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leader in the industry for over 40 years with innovative technologies, unmatched service, competitive pricing, and rapid lead times.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mission: to provide the highest quality products and service to our users at the lowest possible price&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commitment to the development of our employees, including continuous education opportunities like sponsorship for&amp;nbsp;Professional Engineering license and continuous education through weekly webinars and company developed technical videos&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What our employees have to say:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I love the mindset of continuous learning and pushing the bounds of your capabilities&lt;/em&gt; &lt;em&gt;and knowledge. I love the people I work with and the environment, particularly in a world where remote work is common. I love how CaptiveAire is all about connections, with customers, coworkers, end users, and everyone in between.&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Knowing that the company truly has an owner and leadership team that cares for the employees. At CaptiveAire each employee is more than a number, they are a valued member of a growing and diverse team. The open-door policy at CaptiveAire means that no matter who you are in the company that leadership is open to hear your comments and concerns. This means that your ideas are heard. Not once in my time here at CaptiveAire have I felt like I was anything less than an asset to this company and a valued member of the team. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We want to stay on the cutting edge and so are constantly sourcing and utilizing the best equipment available. Any position can provide feedback that is listened to and incorporated into processes. Collaboration is key at CaptiveAire and so there is no being “Silo-ed” into one area.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;CaptiveAire is fast-moving and no-nonsense. We operate differently than any other company that I&#39;ve worked for with our decentralized structure. Quick action is taken when a good idea is presented. We are focused on end users where the rest of the industry is very short-sighted. &lt;strong&gt;We are on the front lines, actively changing the landscape of the HVAC industry.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn more about CaptiveAire and our products &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.captiveaire.com/video-library/&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
