&lt;p&gt;An Application Engineer role encompasses a wide variety of tasks where one day does not look exactly like the next.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Typical tasks can include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exploring different applications and equipment types to help sales engineers meet the requirements of various projects and designs.
