&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CaptiveAire is the nation&#39;s leading manufacturer of commercial kitchen ventilation systems, and now provides a complete solution of fans, heaters, duct work, and HVAC equipment. For over 40 years, we&#39;ve led the industry with innovative technologies, unmatched service, competitive pricing, and rapid lead times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CaptiveAire maintains a network of over 90 sales offices in the U.S. and Canada and six strategically located manufacturing plants in North Carolina, Iowa, Oklahoma, California, Pennsylvania, and Florida.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Due to continued growth, we are looking for a professional Class A CDL Truck Driver to deliver products within the state of North Carolina and beyond.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note: &lt;/strong&gt;Satisfactory background check(criminal and DOT) and negative drug screen required&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monday through Friday with varied hours based on delivery appointments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional work in the plant will be available when delivery appointments are unavailable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Some overnight stays &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;will be required&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive a box truck or low boy to customer sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and schedule delivery appointments to warehouses, job sites, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize pallet jack to assist in offloading of product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage truck and trailer maintenance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep clean and organized truck and trailer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comply with FMCSA and DOT regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional appearance and attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1-2 years’ experience driving a large truck or truck with trailer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid Class A CDL NC driver’s license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean driving record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to regularly lift 50+ lbs. independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional communication skills, dress, and appearance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positive attitude with strong work ethic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable transportation to and from the main facility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or equivalent required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary with monthly bonus based on productivity and profits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jd-section-employer&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jd-description-text&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical, Dental, Vision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;$100,000 Life Insurance &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;Long-Term Disability with Medical election&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible Spending Account (FSA)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401k with employer match&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid holidays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vacation and sick days based upon tenure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jd-section-job-taxonomy-attributes&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;APPLY NOW!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Captive-Aire Systems, Inc. is proud to be an equal opportunity workplace. We review applications for employment without regard to their race, color, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, national origin, ancestry, citizenship, age, uniformed services, genetic information, physical or mental disability, medical condition, marital status, or any other basis prohibited by law.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jd-section-job-type&quot;&gt

&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jd-section-employer&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jd-description-text&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Company Profile:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CaptiveAire is the nation’s leading manufacturer of commercial kitchen ventilation systems, and now provides a complete solution of fans, heaters, ductwork and HVAC equipment. For over 40 years, we’ve led the industry with innovative technologies, unmatched service, competitive pricing, and rapid lead times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CaptiveAire maintains a network of over 90 sales offices in the U.S. and Canada and six strategically located manufacturing plants in North Carolina, Iowa, Oklahoma, California, Pennsylvania and Florida.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Ratliff Metal Spinning, a division of CaptiveAire, is looking for:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ratliff Metal Spinning is hiring Production Workers to work as Machine Operators for our Englewood, Ohio manufacturing facility. If you are looking for meaningful work in a fast-paced, climate-controlled, and financially stable manufacturing environment, we’d love to have you join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note: &lt;/strong&gt;Employment is contingent upon a satisfactory background check and a negative drug screen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monday-Friday 7 a.m. - 3:30 p.m.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Overtime is rare, but may occasionally be required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for individuals who:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates a strong work ethic and willingness to learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possesses basic mechanical aptitude and the ability to use hand and power tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have basic computer and possesses strong organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Works effectively both independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintains reliable attendance and punctuality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follows safety procedures and quality standards consistently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate a variety of CNC and manually controlled metal-forming equipment in accordance with job specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Read and interpret blueprints, technical drawings, and work orders to determine dimensions, tolerances, and production requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and load raw materials and parts into machines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform test runs to ensure machines are operating according to specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set and operate machines to complete full production cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor machine operation throughout production runs to ensure efficiency and consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use precision measuring instruments (calipers, micrometers, gauges, etc.) to inspect finished parts for compliance with specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform routine daily maintenance and report equipment malfunctions as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adhere strictly to company safety policies and established quality control procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in on-the-job training and continuous process improvement initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attendance and punctuality are essential requirements of this position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates honesty and reliability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Works effectively in a team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lift up to 35 lbs. on a continuous basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to lift up to 50 lbs. occasionally and independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess basic math skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office applications, i.e. Word and Excel, preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to follow verbal and written

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated and detail-oriented Collection Specialist to join our team at our corporate office in Raleigh. The ideal candidate will have a background in Finance, Accounting or Economics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Work for CaptiveAire?&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nation’s leading manufacturer of commercial kitchen ventilation systems, and now offering a complete solution of fans, heaters, ductwork and HVAC equipment.  Our primary purpose is to provide fully integrated, sustainable HVAC Systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leader in the industry for over 40 years with innovative technologies, unmatched service, competitive pricing, and rapid lead times.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mission: to provide the highest quality products and service to our users at the lowest possible price&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commitment to the development of our employees.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and manage assigned accounts to ensure timely payment of outstanding customer invoices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contact customers to follow up on overdue balances&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate and resolve billing discrepancies and payment issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Update account stats records and collection efforts in internal systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Report on collection activity and accounts receivable status&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams to resolve account issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in finance, accounting or economics preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recent graduate, customer service, retail or up to 1 year of relevant experience considered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with filing notices and liens on past due projects preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of billing procedures and collection techniques preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of MS office products, Microsoft D365 a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a fast-paced work environment with high volume workload&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
