&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a motivated and detail-oriented employee to join our team at our corporate office in Raleigh. If you like a challenge and enjoy fast-paced work environments this is the role for you. The ideal candidate will have a background in Finance, Accounting or Economics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Work for CaptiveAire?&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nation’s leading manufacturer of commercial kitchen ventilation systems, and now offering a complete solution of fans, heaters, ductwork and HVAC equipment.  Our primary purpose is to provide fully integrated, sustainable HVAC Systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leader in the industry for over 40 years with innovative technologies, unmatched service, competitive pricing, and rapid lead times.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mission: to provide the highest quality products and service to our users at the lowest possible price&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commitment to the development of our employees.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate new credit applications, approve or disapproving requests for credit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct financial analysis including 3&lt;sup&gt;rd&lt;/sup&gt; party report review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish Line of Credit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Approve orders for existing customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and adjust credit lines for existing accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;General accounting support as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in finance, accounting or economics preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recent graduate, or up to 2 years of relevant experience considered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize and manage multiple responsibilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High level of attention to detail and organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of MS office products, Microsoft D365 a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THIS IS NOT A REMOTE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Medical, dental and vision insurance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Disability &amp;amp; life insurance based upon election of medical insurance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401k with employer match&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid holidays&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Paid time off (PTO) based upon tenure&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible spending account (FSA)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
